          <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">¿En cuánto tiempo me responden?</h3>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
